reviewText: Bought this for my daughter who enjoyed the video but said the subtiteling did not match the dialog of the video.

The first 4 episodes of this DVD set are fine there are no problems, however at episode 5 it goes to pieces, the names change to the chinese versions and the subtitles stop making sense, it was the same for episode 6
If i had known the subtitles were like this i would not have purchased this DVD set
